Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花）いきなり\N飛び起きないでください。→
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't wake so suddenly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:57.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,びっくりするじゃないですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:03.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛…　花？\N悪い夢でも見たんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:05.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（心の声）≪どうして　愛花が？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:05.66,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Why is Aika here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪愛花は…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:07.77,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Aika is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花）まだ寝ぼけてます？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:14.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは　夢…　か？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花）「我々は　夢と同じ糸で\N織り上げられている→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.02,Defalics,,0,0,0,,We are such stuff as dreams are made on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:20.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ささやかな一生を\Nしめくくるのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,And our little life is rounded with a sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,眠りなのだ」。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:24.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌な夢を\N見たのなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just had a nightmare, why not go back to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寝直してみては？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:30.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「テンペスト」か。\N（愛花）あら　読んだのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tempest{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, have you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I read it so that I could criticize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:35.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃないと　批評できねぇからな。\N（愛花）やっぱり　まめですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meticulous as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも復讐劇だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another story of revenge, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら　悲劇で終わらなきゃ\Nおかしいじゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it must end in tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:45.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しみは悲しみでしか\N打ち消すことができない。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Only sadness can counter sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら　残される者も\N悲しみでしかねぇだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, all that's left is sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「ああ　苦しくてたまらない」。\Nはぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:52.60,Defalics,,0,0,0,,O! I have suffered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:56.56,Defalics,,0,0,0,,with those that I saw suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:56.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「あんなに\N苦しむ人たちを見ていると！→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,素晴らしい船→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.76,Defalics,,0,0,0,,A brave vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:02.10,Defalics,,0,0,0,,who had, no doubt, some noble creature in her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:02.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと立派な人たちが\N乗っていたのだわ→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.94,Defalics,,0,0,0,,dashed all to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが粉々に砕けて」。
