Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.17,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\bord8\blur8\fs44\pos(640,96)}Episode 13
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.17,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(640,435)}The Reason of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.17,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(640,435)}The Reason of Dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.17,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(675,510)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.17,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(675,510)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そう　これは復讐劇だ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.72,Defalics,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This is a story of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪悲劇を悲劇のまま\N終わらせるための復讐劇≫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:20.46,Defalics,,0,0,0,,A story of revenge, so we can end sadness with sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫（滝川吉野）本当に　そうかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？\N真広→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:31.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は　悲劇で終わらせるために\Nあの旅をしていたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make this journey just to end it in tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,旅？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.21,Defalics,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:39.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そうだ→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　こいつと旅を…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.15,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I was on a journey with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは\N世界を救う旅だったんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we journey so we could save the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.85,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I will save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ナレーション）＜俺が世界を？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:05.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　そんな大それたもんじゃない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing so ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If it saved the world, it would've been the result of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　それは\Nあくまで　ついでだったはず＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((吉野\Nどうして　愛花は殺された？))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.58,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yoshino, why did Aika have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:16.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((くっ…　辻褄が合わない))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.50,Defalics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}It doesn't make sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:23.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　そうだ　俺は愛花を…→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My little sister, Aika, was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妹を殺された＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:30.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((どんな手を使っても\N辻褄を合わせてやる))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:29.49,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes for everything to make sense again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I vowed to find the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜必ず\N犯人を捜し当てると誓った＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　だが　それが　世界を救うことと\Nどうつながる？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but does that relate to saving the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:41.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）((おい　真広\Nこれは　公平な取り引きだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:38.69,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mahiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.70,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This is a fair trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恩を着せられる筋合いはない))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.75,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You have no right to imply that I owe you any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そうは言っても　葉風\N俺がいなくて困るのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.59,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You say that, Hakaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.16,Defalics,,0,0,0,,but you're the one in trouble without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（通信）お前だろ))\N（葉風）((ほう。→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.32,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の妹を殺した犯人を→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.94,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you no longer need me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:56.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が見つけてやらなくても\Nいいというのか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:56.37,Defalics,,0,0,0,,to locate your sister's killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜葉風＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜鎖部葉風＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusaribe Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:05.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　はじまりの樹の加護を受ける\N魔法使い→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The one protected by the Tree of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎖部一族の姫君＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and princess of the Kusaribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　だが　ある日　樽詰めにされ→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, she was stuffed in a barrel and stranded on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,島へ置き去りにされてしまう＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　そこで葉風は　孤島から\N外部へ連絡を取るため→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To contact the outside world from the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:22.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法を込めた人形を瓶に詰めて\N海へ流した＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,she set adrift a magic doll sealed in a bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　それを　俺が拾ったんだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I happened to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:29.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜俺は\N魔法使いと取り引きをした＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a deal with a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　かつて　この世を\N破壊しようとした絶園の樹は→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Exodus once tried to destroy the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹に敗れ\Nその身を封じられた＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but it lost to the Tree of Genesis and was torn apart and sealed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　一方で\Nはじまりの樹も深く傷つき→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Tree of Genesis was also badly damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は　再生のために眠っている＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so it sleeps, waiting to recover, even as it supports this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜鎖部一族の役目は\Nはじまりの樹が→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kusaribe clan's duty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is to prevent the Tree of Exodus from reviving
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再生するときまで\N絶園の樹復活を抑えること＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,before the Tree of Genesis awakens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:57.98,Defalics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Return! Return! Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　だが　一族の代表　鎖部左門は→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the leader of the Kusaribe, Kusaribe Samon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破壊の権化\N絶園の樹の復活をもくろんだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,planned to revive the Tree of Exodus instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, only the princess opposed that plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜葉風だけが　それに抗ったため→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一族から\N追いやられることになったという＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and so, she was forced out of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To revive the Tree of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜絶園の樹の復活には→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it was necessary to gather all the fruits scattered throughout Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:16.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日本中に散らばる果実を\N集める必要があったが…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　それには\N多くの犠牲を伴った＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That caused many victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomenon that occurred wherever a fruit showed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜果実出現の際に発生する\N呪的現象→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Black Iron Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが　黒鉄病と呼ばれるものだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜多くの町や村が壊滅した＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cities fell and people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:40.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　だが　そんなことは\Nどうでもよかった＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't really care about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:43.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜俺は　葉風と取り引きしたんだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a deal with Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I would help her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜俺は　葉風に手を貸して→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのかわり　愛花を殺した犯人を→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and in return, she would use magic to find Aika's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法とやらで見つけろと＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:55.50,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I've already waited a year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺は　もう　１年待ってる→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.62,Defalics,,0,0,0,,to kill Aika's murderer with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花を殺したヤツを\Nこの手で殺すのをな))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:03.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　そう　魔法使いに手を貸して\N世界を救ってやる…→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was helping a mage and saving the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなのは　ついでだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it just happened to coincide with my main goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:09.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((町は　じき封鎖される。\N早く逃げろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The city will be quarantined soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.84,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You should hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜滝川吉野＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Takigawa Yoshino,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,someone I'd shared an ill-fated friendship with since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜ガキのころからの\N腐れ縁だったが→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　ここで\Nこいつと別れるつもりだった＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to say goodbye to him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((じゃあな))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.23,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Well, see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.56,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'll be back after I've killed Aika's murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:23.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((愛花を殺したヤツをぶっ殺したら\N戻ってくる))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そのとき　彼女に会わせろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.69,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Introduce me to your girlfriend then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そうだな))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.57,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:32.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そのときは\Nちゃんと彼女を紹介するよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.43,Defalics,,0,0,0,,When that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.78,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　なのに　あいつは…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:39.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((おっ　助かる。　えっ？))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.96,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yoshino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((お前　バカか!?))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.84,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The hell? Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺につきあう義理はないって\N言っただろ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.14,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I said you didn't have to stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((それがさ→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達を大事にしない人は\N嫌いですって→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.78,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I imagined my girlfriend scolding me and saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.39,Defalics,,0,0,0,,"I dislike people who aren't good to their friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女に怒られそうでね))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.57,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((情けねぇな))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:07:00.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　こうして\N俺と吉野の旅は始まった＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, my journey with Yoshino began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((≫魔法使いは　直接\N倒さなきゃならないだろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.36,Defalics,,0,0,0,,We should fight the mages head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((どういうことだ？))\N((お前と別れたあと→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.11,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,After you left,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:13.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風の魔法で　愛花を殺した野郎が\Nかなり絞れた))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:12.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,we managed to use Hakaze's magic to shorten the list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((犯人は　鎖部一族の誰かだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:15.14,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The killer is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.99,Defalics,,0,0,0,,someone from the Kusaribe clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.15,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The spear guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）((槍男…　ふっ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夏村のことか))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.08,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You mean Natsumura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:29.09,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Tell me your name, mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:29.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）\N((名前を聞かせて　魔法使い))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.05,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I do not have a name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）\N((覚えてもらうほどの名前は→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.04,Defalics,,0,0,0,,important enough for you to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ち合わせていない！))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:43.01,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The Kusaribe clan can borrow power from the Tree of Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜鎖部一族の者は\Nはじまりの樹の理を借り受け→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法を使うことができる＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.90,Defalics,,0,0,0,,to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.01,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Very well, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:51.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）((ならば　姫様\N今日で　その運　尽きさせましょう))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Today, let us put an end to your good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:56.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((左門\Nパンツ一丁でも　私は手ごわいぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.28,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Samon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.24,Defalics,,0,0,0,,even in my underwear, I'm still pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　その　はじまりの樹の加護を\N一身に受ける最強の魔法使い→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The powerful mage who receives the utmost protection
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Tree of Genesis, Kusaribe Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鎖部葉風＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　はじまりの樹の理は\N葉風の理だ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Her reasoning is the Tree of Genesis's reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　あいつが何かを願えば\N樹が　すべて　かなえてしまう＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If she wishes for it, the Tree of Genesis will grant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything is going as Hakaze and the Tree of Genesis planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　すべてが\Nはじまりの樹と葉風の→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いどおりに\N進んでいるとしたら？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((行くぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.43,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ボゥン　ボゥン　ボゥン！))\N((バシューー！))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）((よく来た　少年))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.07,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Welcome, young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:34.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜国防軍が絶園の樹に対して\N総攻撃をかけるなか→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,While the army was fighting the Tree of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we were facing Samon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:38.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは\N鎖部左門と対峙していた＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）((久しいな　左門。→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.49,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Samon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.93,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Four months now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:45.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４か月ぶりになるか。\N変わりなくやっているようだな))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.26,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Seems you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ふっ　姫様こそ→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.21,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You, too, Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:51.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（通信）遠く隔たっていても\Nお変わりなく))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.96,Defalics,,0,0,0,,despite being so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜葉風が用意していた\N特製の魔具を持って→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With that powerful talisman Hakaze made,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:59.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが　この地に来た時点で\N勝敗は決していたはずだったが…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,our victory should have been guaranteed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment we arrived, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Samon told us that it was actually the Tree of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜絶園の樹ではなく→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹が　むしろ\N世界を滅ぼすかもしれないと→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the Tree of Exodus, that would destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門は言った＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But I actually don't give a crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　だが　俺には\Nそんなことは　どうでもいい＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((世界の心配は　あとだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.03,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'll worry about the world later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:17.03,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Now, get Hakaze back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((さあ　葉風を戻せよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:21.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　そうだ\N世界を救うなんて　二の次だ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving the world comes later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺は　あいつに\N見つけてもらうヤツがいる))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.78,Defalics,,0,0,0,,There's someone she needs to find for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　なのに…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:34.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((姫様　今は何年です？))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:34.09,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Princess, what year is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((今は　西暦…))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.84,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜鎖部の姫君は→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess was trapped in the time prison two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２年前の時間の檻に\N封じ込められていた＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:49.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜今現在は　骨になってるんなら\Nここへは　戻りようがない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If she was already a bunch of bones, bringing her back was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜葉風との契約も\Nここまでだった＞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And my deal with Hakaze would end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((残念だったな　葉風))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.41,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Too bad, Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((まあ　骨になってるんなら\Nしかたねぇ))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.32,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing we can do if you're just bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そこで勝手に死んでろ))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.45,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just die there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:07.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　だったら\N取り引き相手を変えるだけだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:07.24,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Then I merely need to deal with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:11.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜愛花を殺した犯人が分かれば\Nそれでいいからな＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:11.29,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Because all that matters to me is finding Aika's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:15.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((分かった。\Nお前の要求に応じよう))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:13.51,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.92,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I will grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:19.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　これで\N取り引き成立のはずだったが…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The deal should have been sealed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.59,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ごめん　真広))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:26.85,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ちょっと　その魔具を\N渡してもらおうと思ってね！))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:29.69,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd borrow that talisman for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:41.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((真広\Nこちらの側につくというなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:41.11,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Mahiro, if you'll switch back to this side,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に　愛花ちゃんの彼氏が\N誰だったか教えてやる))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:45.00,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the identity of Aika's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:48.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜吉野が　愛花の彼氏が\N誰だか知ってると→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino suddenly said he knew who Aika's boyfriend was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:50.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぬかしやがった＞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.29,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You really know who it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ああ　知ってる。　でも真広→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.16,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.74,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But, Mahiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の話に乗らないかぎり→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:58.39,Defalics,,0,0,0,,unless you agree to my terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かは　一生　教えない))
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:00.26,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I will never tell you who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:05.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((お前は　誰か知らないまま\N一生　悩むことになるぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:05.29,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You'll be left ignorant of who it was forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.01,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I won't agree that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　それは　ごめんだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:12.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜吉野のヤツ　とんでもない\N奥の手を隠し持ってたわけだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.72,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Damn it, Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was holding the ultimate trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜何を思ったか→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野は　葉風をここに戻すことが\N可能だと立証するために→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but to prove the fact that it was possible to bring Hakaze back,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:23.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱弁を振るいだした＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he started a debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　でたらめな論理だったが→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though his logic was weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へこんだお姫様を\N奮い立たせるには十分だったろう＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it was enough to lift the depressed princess's spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:34.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬・通信）((左門殿→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:32.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Mr. Samon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:38.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１年前に殺人を犯した者の調査が\N終わりました))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,We've concluded the investigation into the murder a year ago by one in the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:41.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そうか！\N犯人が特定できたか！))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:39.73,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.42,Defalics,,0,0,0,,So you've found the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　だが　ここまでだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.43,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But that's the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:48.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜犯人が分かれば\N葉風が戻る戻らないは関係ない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.67,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If I learn who killed Aika,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:48.60,Defalics,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter to me whether Hakaze is here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬・通信）((それが左門殿…→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.10,Defalics,,0,0,0,,However, Mr. Samon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.48,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The killer is not in the clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犯人は　一族内にいないのです！))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:02.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((いるかもしれん))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.99,Defalics,,0,0,0,,There may be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((いるかもしれんのだ…→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:07.72,Defalics,,0,0,0,,one person who could have escaped the web of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ一人\N魔法の網にかからぬ者が！))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((いや　破壊こそが理の者が！))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:10.58,Defalics,,0,0,0,,No, someone whose logic is destruction itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((いわば　絶園の魔法使いが！))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,In other words... the mage of Exodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜絶園の樹は　この世で唯一→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Exodus is the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:23.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の理を\N超える力を持つ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with power that can surpass the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜愛花は　その絶園の魔法使いに\N殺されたのか？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this mage of Exodus kill Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　それとも\N俺と葉風を結び付けるために→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was she killed by the Tree of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹によって\N殺されたのか？＞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to bring Hakaze and me together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:36.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((たとえ\N本当に　はじまりの樹が→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:38.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Even if the Tree of Genesis really did cause Mahiro's sister's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広の妹の死を\N招いたのだとしても→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I must go back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　そちらに戻らねばならん))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:45.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((戻らねば　何もできん。\N何も償えん))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.12,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I can do nothing until I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.90,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I cannot make any amends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　どちらにせよ　まずは\N葉風が時間の檻を破って→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how things go,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if Hakaze doesn't break free from the prison of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここへ戻ってこないと\N話は進まない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Only after that will we be able to determine the killer's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜誰が犯人か決めるのは\Nそれからだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:25.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）((我が名は　鎖部葉風))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.15,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I am Kusaribe Hakaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.19,Defalics,,0,0,0,,the Princess of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:28.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((はじまりの姫宮))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((２年の時を越え　帰って来たぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I've traveled two years through time to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは…。\N≫思い出した？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:47.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は…。　俺とお前は　このあと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.84,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）((はぁ　はぁ　はぁ))\N((吉野!!))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.44,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行かないで！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:13.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり　俺は死んだんだな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I really did die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花の声）あら　まだですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.89,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Oh, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　何を言って…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花の声）\N真広も言っていたでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.83,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself, Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この物語は\N悲劇では終わらないんです。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This story doesn't end in tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{ Part B }
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また夢か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,dreaming again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:52.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉…　野？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やあ。\Nやあじゃねぇよ！　彼氏は!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "Hey" me! Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:58.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花の彼氏は誰なんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was Aika's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのあと　どうなったか知りたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know what happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのあと？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:15.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだよ。　みんな死んじゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:18.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹が\N全部　飲み込んじゃったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis swallowed them all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹は　世界中に現れて→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis appeared across the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and swallowed up all the cities and the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,町も人も飲み込んじゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Armies, worldwide, went to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:34.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから\N世界中の軍隊が反撃に出たんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But none of them returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　みんな帰って来なかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:43.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹に\N吸収されちまったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the Tree of Genesis absorb them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:46.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち向かうものは\Nみんな飲み込まれちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that opposed it was swallowed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６０億－２０億は？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's six billion minus two billion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:53.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？　４０億だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Four billion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the current world population.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:56.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが今の全世界の人口。\Nあっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:16:01.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった数時間で　たくさん壊されて\Nたくさん殺されたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Many places were destroyed, and many people were killed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in a matter of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:05.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ　後片づけが大変そうだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like cleaning that up would suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:10.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだ人も残されたものも\Nみんな消えちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead have all vanished, along with anything left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree ate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部　樹に食べられちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:20.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食べられたのは　はじまりの樹を\N攻撃したものばかりじゃないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ones the Tree ate weren't limited to those who attacked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紛争中の地域とか\N暴動が起こっている所にも→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It appeared in areas affected by hardship and rebellion, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,樹は出現した。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,町なかでも　戦闘行為があれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in cities with mere intentions of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:32.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを察知して\Nはじまりの樹が出てくるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree of Genesis sensed that fact and appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　誰も戦争をしなくなった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So no one starts wars anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:39.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,樹は\N小さな犯罪も見ているらしいんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree also seems to monitor minor crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,略奪や暴動を起こしても\N樹は現れる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to robbers and rebels, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we started fighting, it could appear before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:47.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで　僕と真広がケンカしても\N出てくるかもしれないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今　世界は　すごく平和なんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is very peaceful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？\Nお土産。　コンビニで買ってきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got them at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれから７日くらいでね\N買えるようになったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It took around seven days to be able to buy these again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Water and electricity were restored, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,止まってた電気や水道も\N復旧したんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構なことじゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that sounds pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけじゃない。　見て。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:16.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは？\Nこれも　世界中で見られる現象。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a worldwide phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Deserts turned into forests,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,砂漠は森になったし→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and polluted seas returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,汚かった海も\N元どおりに戻っていってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:26.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　水不足や食料問題まで\N解決しちゃいそうなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we're on the brink of resolving food and water shortages in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:30.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　そりゃ。\Nはじまりの樹様様じゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like we should be \N praising the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:34.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれから　絶園の樹も\N動かなくなっちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Exodus stopped moving afterwards, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any fruits in sight, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:36.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,果実も　一つも飛んでないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不合理だな。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's irrational.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has been saved without my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界は　勝手に救われたが→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but things still don't make any sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ　俺の辻褄が合わない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり\N悲劇は悲劇で終わらせたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really do want to end a tragedy with a tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,復讐を遂げないと終わらない？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be satisfied unless you get your revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:02.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　そうだ　俺は愛花の…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find Aika's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:19.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((ちっ。　また愛花のお小言を\N聞かなきゃならねぇのか))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.18,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Do I really have to listen to Aika talk crazy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((愛…　花？　はぁ～))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:53.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((何やってんだよ　お前\Nこんなとこで…))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜誰が信じられるだろう＞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.23,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Who would have believed the sight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:05.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜彼女に咲いた赤い花＞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:05.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,of the red flower that bloomed from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:21.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　こんなにも冷たい　その肌＞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.35,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Her skin felt so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　それでも分からなかった→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:26.39,Defalics,,0,0,0,,And yet, I couldn't believe that Aika was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで\N愛花が死んでいるだなんて＞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜　なぜなら…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.11,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜俺は知らない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:38.30,Defalics,,0,0,0,,While Aika was alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,＜命ある愛花→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.10,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I never knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その肌の柔らかさを　ぬくもりを→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:48.32,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The softness of her skin, her warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:48.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　一度だって知らない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ～。\N≪ガチャ（ドアの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い夢でも見たか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Samon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門か。\N寝覚めに見るには最悪なツラだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the worst face to see when waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開口一番　それか。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the first thing you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How long was I asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:29.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どのくらい　俺は寝てた？\N（左門）約１か月だ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,About a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと早く起こせもしたが\N状況が状況だけにな→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have woken you earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but circumstances are as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔法の効果で　しばらく\N寝たままでいてもらった。→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I had you stay asleep with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪く思うな。\Nん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹か。\N（左門）ああ　その一部だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Tree of Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A portion of it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も聞かないんだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:59.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢で見たとおりだ。　はっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野は!?　吉野は無事か!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yoshino? Is he safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting separately, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:06.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）我らと別行動ではあるが\N心配ない。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前より健康で\Nお前より頭が回っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's much more healthy and intelligent than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で　なんで　俺を生かした。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Why'd you keep me alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に何をさせたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）不破真広→
