Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:05.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）オーライ　オーライ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ストップ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オッケーです。　ふぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.27,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪（同僚）\N羽村さ～ん　休憩ですよ～。→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanemura, it's lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:17.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女に振られた!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend dumped you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）将来性のない\N頼りない人なんかいらないって。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she didn't want someone so irresponsible, without a future...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:26.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えぐいですね。\Nはぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:32.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　話は変わるんですけど\N絶園の魔法使いのうわさって→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, on a different subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the rumor about the mage of Exodus?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたことあります？\Nあっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:36.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（同僚）\Nなんでも　あの樹を壊して→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They say one exists and might be able to destroy that Tree, and return everything to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:38.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界を元どおりにできる\N魔法使いが→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.99,0:23:41.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるとか　いないとか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:43.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）\Nああ　それ　たぶん　僕のことだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're probably talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえ～。　はっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:53.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羽村）世界を救ったら→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I saved the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you think I'd have a future?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕にも　将来性　出てくるかな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hakaze has a crush on Yoshino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風が吉野にほれた!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that he has a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.31,0:24:06.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）聞けば　あやつ\N彼女もいるというではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:08.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）今や姫様は→
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the princess' thoughts revolve around Takigawa Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,滝川吉野を中心に\N物事を考えているのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）私の知ったことか！\Nはぁ～。　つまり…。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.29,0:24:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:19.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）滝川吉野が\N絶園の魔法使いである可能性に。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.82,0:24:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Takigawa Yoshino may be the mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:21.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）いつ　その力に気付いた？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.01,0:24:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you realize this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　しかたありませんか。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there's no other choice...
